<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hello=
 All,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Refer=
ring to your email below of December 9.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Are y=
ou able to indicate the status of the undertaking of your independent invest=
igations as proposed below.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We ha=
ve received 3 tender responses back from the reinstatement service providers=
 who attended site with Raffaella and myself late last year.<o:p></o:p></spa=
n></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">As we=
 are all aware we have received these tender responses based on the scope of=
 works provided by ASURNZ and subsequently shared with all parties.<o:p></o:=
p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Agree=
ment on the scope of works is paramount to claim progression. If we can move=
 to determine the agreed scope for claim related loss =E2=80=93 we can move q=
uickly afterwards to provide the final outcome.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I loo=
k forward to an update on your independent enquiries.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Thank=
 you very much.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regar=
ds,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant=
. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>=
