<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hello=
 Raffaella,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I tru=
st this email finds you well.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Follo=
wing on from email last Monday - I would like to receive your permission to b=
egin the process of obtaining preliminary tender responses for your claim.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">It wo=
uld be a significant progression if I could work with tender respondents and=
 begin the tendering process before the beginning of the Christmas break.<o:=
p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Pleas=
e advise me if I have your permission to begin this process.<o:p></o:p></spa=
n></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Many T=
hanks,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant=
. &nbsp;&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp=
