<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><o:p>&nbsp;</o:p></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hi St=
ephen,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Below=
 is a copy of an email which I sent to all parties this afternoon outlaying t=
he expected time frames of the results which will be available to be shared w=
ith all regarding test results from
 23 Mays Street, Devonport.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>=
&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Prior=
 to receiving the report from the forensic testing =E2=80=93 I am keen to ta=
ke whatever steps I can to progress the claim.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Preli=
minary results and findings suggest that we may have a relatively complete u=
nderstanding of what the final scope of works will be to fully remediate the=
 property under the claim.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>=
&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">If we=
 accept on a preliminary basis that the scope of works required to remediate=
 the property is
<b><u>generally defined</u></b> as follows:<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>=
&nbsp;</o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Ba=
sement Level</span></u><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>=
</o:p></span></p>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l1 level1 lfo4"><span lang=3D=
"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clean and decontaminate all exposed inter=
nal brick surfaces to ground level of dwelling<o:p></o:p></span></li><li cla=
ss=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l1 level1 lfo4"><span lang=3D"EN-U=
S" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Replace charred timber framework to midfloor s=
tructure and ground floor walls as required<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D=
"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l1 level1 lfo4"><span lang=3D"EN-US" st=
yle=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Rebuild rear deck and steps to match existing
<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l1 l=
evel1 lfo4"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Replace all hard=
wood decking boards to internal balcony
<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l1 l=
evel1 lfo4"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clean and encaps=
ulate all timber structural components to ground-floor walls and midfloor st=
ructure as required<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" sty=
le=3D"mso-list:l1 level1 lfo4"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0p=
t">Replace midfloor insulation<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListPar=
agraph" style=3D"mso-list:l1 level1 lfo4"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font=
-size:11.0pt">Replace ceiling linings to ground floor as required<o:p></o:p>=
</span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l1 level1 lfo4"=
><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Supply and install rear ped=
estrian door to rear of ground floor<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoL=
istParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l1 level1 lfo4"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D=
"font-size:11.0pt">Clean and repaint bi-folding basement doors to ground flo=
or<o:p></o:p></span></li></ul>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Se=
cond Level<o:p></o:p></span></u></p>
<ul type=3D"disc">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l11 level1 lfo5"><span lang=
