 class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l11 level1 lfo5"><span lang=3D=
"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clean and decontaminate all interior bric=
k surfaces in the exterior wall cavities<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"=
