yle=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Encapsulate all timber framing to all exposed walls=
<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"mso-list:l11 l=
evel1 lfo5"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Re-line all expo=
sed walls with new gib-board wall linings. Gib-stop and sand to L4<o:p></o:p=
