span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Remove, dispose of existing r=
oof cladding<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"m=
argin-left:-4.5pt;mso-list:l9 level1 lfo6"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"fon=
t-size:11.0pt">Supply and install new roofing cladding to match existing<o:p=
></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:-4.5p=
t;mso-list:l9 level1 lfo6"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">S=
upply and install new PVC spouting and downpipes<o:p></o:p></span></li><li c=
lass=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:-4.5pt;mso-list:l9 level1 lfo=
6"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Clean and repaint soffits=
<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-left:-=
4.5pt;mso-list:l9 level1 lfo6"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0p=
t">Clean and repaint fascia board<o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoList=
