<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp=
;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I wil=
l need to discuss the above with you in some detail, accepting that you may m=
ake corrections as required =E2=80=93 however once we have discussed the
<b><i><u>draft proposed scope</u></i></b> I will request that you provide To=
wer Insurance with a draft copy of the scope at which we arrive, and an acco=
mpanying cost estimate for reserving and quoting purposes.<o:p></o:p></span>=
</p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Let=E2=
=80=99s talk tomorrow when we can.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Many T=
hanks,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant=
