<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Good a=
fternoon Raffaella &amp; All,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I hav=
e just spoken with Abigail Collin re the forthcoming test results.<o:p></o:p=
></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We ex=
pect the test results to be available to share with all parties by the end o=
f next week. I have chased the provider to expedite this.
<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The p=
reliminary report from the Forensic Testing will contain the =E2=80=98raw da=
ta=E2=80=99 from the laboratory results, and the locations of the sample sit=
es from where the tests were conducted.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">As pr=
omised this preliminary report will be shared with all as soon as it is rece=
ived and it will be followed by a fuller report which will provide Towers po=
sition on the findings of the report.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Thank=
 you for your continued patience.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Regar=
ds,<o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Grant=
. <o:p></o:p></span></p>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt"><o:p>=
