<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal">&nbsp;<span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Hello=
 Raffaella,</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Thank=
 you for the email below.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We ca=
n confirm that testing can commence at 2pm on Friday October 17.</span><span=
 lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">We wi=
ll test from sample sites as required to complete a full and thorough determ=
ination of any potential contamination, inclusive of all the areas which you=
 have referred to below.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">You m=
ay undertake your own independent testing at any stage; however, Tower would=
 only consider reimbursement for testing which is - a) claim related &amp; b=
) testing which is outside of that which
 Tower will complete.<span class=3D"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span></sp=
an><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I am c=
onfident that the Tower Insurance testing will be transparent, quantified by=
 lab results, and adequate to provide comfort for all parties.</span><span l=
ang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp=
;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Cl=
arified scope of testing as follows:</span></u><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o=
:p></span></p>
</div>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0cm" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;mso=
-list:l10 level1 lfo11">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">150mm diameter inspection po=
rtals cut in wall cavities of every room on the first floor at a height of 3=
00 mm of floor level and directly underneath the top plate.</span><span lang=
=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"ma=
rgin-top:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;mso-list:l10 level1 lfo11">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Testing of the roof cavity a=
t the soffit junction where potential contaminants may have risen through th=
e wall cavity. Testing of the roof cavity at the apex where smoke may have a=
ccumulated.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"M=
soListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;mso-list:l10 leve=
l1 lfo11">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Testing of the underside of t=
he rear large upper deck.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></li>=
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;mso=
-list:l10 level1 lfo11">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Testing of the basement util=
izing all exposed framing cavities and 150mm testing portals cut into any re=
mining ceiling linings in the basemen area.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>=
</o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0cm;mar=
gin-bottom:0cm;mso-list:l10 level1 lfo11">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Any additional sample sites t=
hat we feel are required during testing. &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span lang=
=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></li></ol>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp=
;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><u><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">To=
 ensure effectual testing it would be beneficial if you could confirm the fo=
llowing:</span></u><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<ol style=3D"margin-top:0cm" start=3D"1" type=3D"1">
<li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;mso=
-list:l3 level1 lfo12">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">That the chlorine was locate=
d in the laundry room downstairs at the time of the fire.</span><span lang=3D=
"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margi=
n-top:0cm;margin-bottom:0cm;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo12">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The quantity of the chlorine=
 that was in that room at the time of the fire.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><=
o:p></o:p></span></li><li class=3D"MsoListParagraph" style=3D"margin-top:0cm=
;margin-bottom:0cm;mso-list:l3 level1 lfo12">
<span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Where there any<span class=3D=
"apple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span><u>other chemicals</u><span class=3D"ap=
ple-converted-space">&nbsp;</span>that were located in that same room, or an=
ywhere else downstairs. &nbsp;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span>=
</li></ol>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp=
;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp=
;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Beyon=
d completing testing and providing laboratory results as described above, I a=
m certain the most productive action we can make towards progressing the cla=
im is to have a meeting where we can
 discuss the overall claim response process, providing a forum for you to ta=
ble any questions, or concerns that you may hold. Those concerns can be resp=
onded to, and the responses can be documented via minutes with actions and a=
greements detailed in the minutes
 providing a framework for moving forward with a pre-agreed and productive p=
athway. I believe this would be very worthwhile and will provide us all with=
 detail, clarity, and documentation that we can all use to our benefit.</spa=
n><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Your l=
awyers and advisors would of course be welcome to attend this meeting.</span=
><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp=
;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I loo=
k forward to seeing you again on Friday.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o=
:p></span></p>
</div>
<div>
