 pm works for me, and I=E2=80=99d appreciate it if testing and assessment co=
uld be scheduled accordingly. I also reserve my right to undertake</span><sp=
an lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:1.0pt;color:w=
hite">&nbsp;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
