<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Thank you for your email and for=
 confirming receipt of our letter.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Friday, 17 October after 2:00 pm=
 works for me, and I=E2=80=99d appreciate it if testing and assessment could=
 be scheduled accordingly.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">I also reserve my right to under=
take independent testing and assessment of the property to ensure a full and=
 impartial evaluation.<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Having reviewed the proposed pla=
n, I=E2=80=99m concerned the current testing schedule appears incomplete. It=
 does not include the first floor, roof cavity, or the large upper deck, and=
 the basement coverage seems partial, given
 the known extent of smoke, water, and chemical contamination.<o:p></o:p></s=
pan></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">I therefore request confirmation=
 that the planned inspection and sampling will be expanded to include all le=
vels and relevant structural areas. Alternatively, please confirm that Tower=
 will meet my reasonable costs should
 I need to arrange independent specialists to carry out supplementary testin=
g (including laboratory analysis).<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">Please confirm the final timing f=
or the 17th and the revised scope of testing once available.<o:p></o:p></spa=
n></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US">&nbsp;<o:p></o:p></span></p>
