<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I hav=
e requested that the appointed specialists provide dates and times when they=
 can be available.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I am p=
roposing that the following persons complete site visit, assessing &amp; tes=
ting, as a necessary pre-requisite to providing relevant reports for all sta=
keholders to review:</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp=
;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Gr=
ant Metson</span></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span lang=3D"EN-=
US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=3D"EN-US" styl=
e=3D"font-size:11.0pt">=E2=80=93 Regional Assessing Manager</span><span lang=
