ephen Walker</span></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span lang=3D"E=
N-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=3D"EN-US" st=
yle=3D"font-size:11.0pt">=E2=80=93 Technical Building Consultant.
 ASURNZ.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Wa=
rwick Banks</span></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span lang=3D"EN=
-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=3D"EN-US" sty=
le=3D"font-size:11.0pt">=E2=80=93 Associate Structural Engineer.
 CPEng</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Al=
exandra Dalzell</span></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span lang=3D=
"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=3D"EN-US" s=
tyle=3D"font-size:11.0pt">=E2=80=93 Forensic Scientist</span><span lang=3D"E=
N-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Ty=
rell Craig</span></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span lang=3D"EN-=
US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=3D"EN-US" styl=
e=3D"font-size:11.0pt">=E2=80=93 Restoration Cleaning Specialist.</span><spa=
n lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><b><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">LB=
P Builder</span></b><span class=3D"apple-converted-space"><span lang=3D"EN-U=
S" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp;</span></span><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=
=3D"font-size:11.0pt">[ unconfirmed individual ] =E2=80=93
 we will require the builder to cut inspection holes in the wall linings so t=
esting can be completed within the wall cavities.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"=
><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp=
;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">The i=
ntention is to test for smoke and chemical contamination within the wall cav=
ities, and on the exposed surfaces downstairs. There will be a significant n=
umber of sample sites [tests] to be
 completed to be able to author a reliable report. After initial testing is c=
ompleted, our intention is to apply restorative cleaning methods to targeted=
 individual sample sites, followed by subsequent testing, post-cleaning, to p=
rovide data to measure the
 effectiveness of cleaning/decontamination.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p>=
</o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">All s=
amples taken from site will require laboratory analysis before being incorpo=
rated into a report. This process may take up to 10 working days =E2=80=93 s=
o we want to capture swab samples from surfaces
 before and after the decontamination process is undertaken.</span><span lan=
g=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp=
;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">At th=
is stage we are looking like being able to conduct this testing onsite, as w=
ell as CPEng site visit for assessment, on Friday October 17. Time to yet be=
 confirmed.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp=
;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">I am u=
nsure from your letter attached whether Raffaella and/or other nominated par=
ties wish to be present while this testing and assessment is being conducted=
. Can you please confirm for me so
 that I can complete arrangements that will suit all parties who need to be p=
resent.</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">&nbsp=
;</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
<div>
<div>
<p class=3D"MsoNormal"><span lang=3D"EN-US" style=3D"font-size:11.0pt">Many T=
hanks,</span><span lang=3D"EN-US"><o:p></o:p></span></p>
</div>
</div>
